*Signa sequimur, veritatem quaerimus*
*Manus mundae, mens attenta*
*Sanitatis custodes sumus*
 
Wash thy palms with measured care
Twenty seconds, time to spare
Before the patient, after too
This vital rite we must pursue
 
*Tempus numeratum, rituale servatum*
*In ablutione, constantia*
 
*Signa sequimur, veritatem quaerimus*
*Manus mundae, mens attenta*
*Sanitatis custodes sumus*
 
Each device we sanitize
Between each case we recognize
The time of contact must suffice
microbes to be neutralized
 
*Instrumenta pura, cura secura*
*In diligentia, excellentia*
 
*Signa sequimur, veritatem quaerimus*
*Manus mundae, mens attenta*
*Sanitatis custodes sumus*
 
Beneath our sight they multiply
In matrix walls they fortify
Each catheter and line deny
Their colonizing battle cry
 
*Invisibilia vincimus scientia*
*In persistentia, victoria*
 
*Signa sequimur, veritatem quaerimus*
*Manus mundae, mens attenta*
*Sanitatis custodes sumus*
 
When vessels empty stand in shame
Let not neglect bring us to blame
The sanitizer's empty frame
Must swift attention now reclaim
*Vasa vacua, pericula vera*
*Repleatur sine mora*
 
*Signa sequimur, veritatem quaerimus*
*Manus mundae, mens attenta*
*Sanitatis custodes sumus*
 
While waters flow across our hands
We contemplate infection's strands
Each patient's risk we understand
As tubes and lines we wisely scan
 
*Mens intentiva, cura preventiva*
*In sapientia, prudentia*
 
*Signa sequimur, veritatem quaerimus*
*Manus mundae, mens attenta*
*Sanitatis custodes sumus*
 
Don the gown and mask with care
For droplet, contact, and the air
Standard precautions everywhere
Each barrier we must prepare
 
*Signa dubia, protectio certa*
*Melius praevenire quam poenitere*
 
*Signa sequimur, veritatem quaerimus*
*Manus mundae, mens attenta*
*Sanitatis custodes sumus*
 
With kindness do we guide the way
When protocols begin to stray
No judgment cast, no harsh display
But gentle words that seem to say
Together we maintain the way
That keeps infection's spread at bay
 
*Verba lenia, effectus magna*
*In harmonia, efficacia*
 
*Signa sequimur, veritatem quaerimus*
*Manus mundae, mens attenta*
*Sanitatis custodes sumus*
 
*In purificatione est salus*
*Per scientiam, absolutio*
*Eternam vigilantiam*
*Pro sanitate omnium*
